<plot>Elijah, a young Black grocery store bagger, walks a Hasidic Jewish customer to his car during the height of the racially motivated Crown Heights riots in Brooklyn, New York. African-American customers threaten the Jewish customer's life because of the racial tensions that flare in this largely Jewish/Black neighborhood.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?119653</url></doc>
